comment: Smith (ORL) maintains legal guarding position while defending Millsap (ATL) on his drive and shot attempt.
Horford (ATL) makes contact to Payton's (ORL) head during his shot attempt.

R-Slash shows Payton (ORL) picks up his dribble while on both feet (his right toe is still touching the floor). He establishes his right foot as his pivot when he lifts his left foot from the floor before passing.
Horford (ATL) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly deflects the inbound pass away from Vucevic (ORL).
LATR shows Horford (ATL) extends his leg and hip into Gordon's (ORL) path, without giving him room to avoid the screen and delivering contact.
LATR shows Gordon's (ORL) arms are not vertical as he defends Millsap (ATL) during his shot attempt attempt.
Horford (ATL) and Vucevic (ORL) briefly engage during the inbound pass.
ATL does not inbound the ball or call the timeout before five seconds elapses.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the shot was taken before the game clock expired was upheld.
Teague (ATL) makes contact to the arm of Gordon (ORL) that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Gordon (ORL) jumps A to B and makes contact with Teague (ATL), affecting his shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling that Teague's (ATL) shot was taken from behind the three-point line was upheld.
Vucevic (ORL) and Millsap (ATL) make incidental contact when they attempt to retrieve the loose ball.
Horford (ATL) maintains legal guarding position when defending Vucevic's (ORL) shot attempt.
Horford (ATL) makes contact with Fournier's (ORL) arm.
Horford (ATL) dislodges Vucevic (ORL) in the post.
Fournier (ORL) makes contact to Korver (ATL), affecting his freedom of movement off ball.
Horford (ATL) grabs the hip of Vucevic (ORL) which affects his freedom of movement off ball.
Horford (ATL) gives Fournier (ORL) room to avoid the contact on the off ball screen.
RHH shows Fournier (ORL) initiates legal contact on the start of his drive with Bazemore (ATL). The contact is not, by itself, enough to dislodge Bazemore from his legal guarding position.
Bazemore (ATL) commits a take foul on Oladipo (ORL).
Millsap (ATL) and Vucevic (ORL) engage for the long rebound.
Millsap (AT) commits the take foul on Oladipo (ORL).
